        <title type="html"><![CDATA[题解 CF837A 【Text Volume】]]></title>
        <id>https://blog.wangdemao.cf/post/ti-jie-cf837a-text-volume/</id>
        <link href="https://blog.wangdemao.cf/post/ti-jie-cf837a-text-volume/">
        </link>
        <updated>2020-05-21T03:13:14.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="1思路">1.思路</h2>
<ol>
<li>先求出每个单词里大写的数量，放在 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>c</mi><mi>a</mi><msub><mi>p</mi><mi>i</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">cap_i</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">c</span><span class="mord mathdefault">a</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault">p</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.31166399999999994em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 里。</li>
<li>在求出 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>c</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>p</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">cap</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">c</span><span class="mord mathdefault">a</span><span class="mord mathdefault">p</span></span></span></span> 数组里的最大值，输出。</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="2知识点">2.知识点</h2>
<ol>
<li>在头文件 <cctype> 中有一个函数 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>i</mi><mi>s</mi><mi>u</mi><mi>p</mi><mi>p</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>r</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">isupper</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.85396em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">i</span><span class="mord mathdefault">s</span><span class="mord mathdefault">u</span><span class="mord mathdefault">p</span><span class="mord mathdefault">p</span><span class="mord mathdefault">e</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span></span></span></span> ，如果字符是大写，该函数返回1，否则返回0。</li>
<li>用以下代码可以不间断的输入：</li>
</ol>
<pre><code class="language-cpp">while(cin&gt;&gt;t)
{
  //do something...
}
</code></pre>
<h2 id="3实现">3.实现</h2>
<p><strong>先看找单词里的大写字母：</strong></p>
<pre><code class="language-cpp">int cap[201]={};

void findcap(string t,int no)
{
  for(int i=0;i&lt;t.size();i++)
  {
  	if(isupper(t[i]))
  		cap[no]++;
  }
}

</code></pre>
<p><strong>找最大：</strong></p>
<pre><code class="language-cpp">int getmax(int no)
{
   int max=-1;
   
   for(int i=0;i&lt;=no;i++)
   {
   	if(max&lt;cap[i])
   		max=cap[i];
   }
   return max;
}

</code></pre>
<p><strong>主函数：</strong></p>
<pre><code class="language-cpp">int main()
{
	string t;
	int no=0;
	
	int n;
	
	cin&gt;&gt;n;
	
	while(cin&gt;&gt;t)
	{
		//no++;
		findcap(t,no);
		no++;
	}
	
	cout&lt;&lt;getmax(no);
	
	return 0;
}
</code></pre>
]]></content>
